{"tid":660553,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"朋友個仔先天性有病.....","createTime":"2018-05-10T18:56:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-11T03:10:06.000Z","uid":133989,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"733e2e554f80648519211eca117cbba4d5db41c1","tid":660553,"uid":133989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T18:56:48.000Z","msg":"唉是咁的<br />\n個FD個仔宜家先4個月大，已經因為先天性既病做過5次大手術啦.....<br />\n佢個病好似係同腎同輸尿管有關，唔記得個學術名啦.....<br />\n重點係一次手術就要30萬.....頭一個月大已經開始做啦....<br />\n宜家日日要打針，住院，日日3000蚊呀....<br />\n大人就話可以買保險幫輕下<br />\n咁細既仲要先天性保險都唔收<br />\n唉，真係好想幫下佢，想知會唔會有人知政府有冇咩醫療援助去幫呢類既情況?<br />\n我真係好想幫輕下佢，始終咁多年朋友....<br />\n但係呢種情況發現自己可以做既真係好有限....<br />\n有人聽過或知道類似事件同解決方法既分享下......"},{"pid":"2655c1a7163d85491bc94aee272388f130e20cb2","tid":660553,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:01:01.000Z","msg":"無能為力,只能祝福"},{"pid":"cc2e2d20b89953c1baff05b09f8a232b00a0a140","tid":660553,"uid":133989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2655c1a7163d85491bc94aee272388f130e20cb2","tid":660553,"uid":21488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:01:01.000Z","msg":"無能為力,只能祝福"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThx sis"},{"pid":"bb9aedfbc37dc0bb1fa1ef10ab645903edeb9caf","tid":660553,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:14:27.000Z","msg":"睇錯先天有性病....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw無得產前check到？"},{"pid":"6d347bd7313407096e65b4a13cb87104b12792c1","tid":660553,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:14:45.000Z","msg":"呢個病佢長大左會唔會有咩生活影響<br />\nBtw 祝福"},{"pid":"5bf5f97fbb8fdb0e03b942eaf786c7037fbccafa","tid":660553,"uid":129599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T19:15:20.000Z","msg":"政府醫院唔包??"},{"pid":"978b172306cf20c9fc4f2eb6e3ae1ce61c43d949","tid":660553,"uid":133989,"like":0,"dis